# ==========================================
# DINEFLOW MONOREPO .GITIGNORE
# Applies to all microservices automatically
# ==========================================

# 1. Virtual Environments
**/.venv/
**/venv/
**/env/

# 2. Environment Variables & Secrets (CRITICAL)
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/*firebase-credentials*.json
**/*firebase-adminsdk*.json
**/service_account.json
**/jwt_keys/*.pem
**/*.pem

# 3. Python & Django
**/__pycache__/
**/*.py[cod]
**/*$py.class
**/db.sqlite3
**/db.sqlite3-journal
**/media/
**/staticfiles/

# 4. Testing & Coverage
**/.pytest_cache/
**/.coverage
**/htmlcov/

# 6. OS Generated Files
**/.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store?
**/._*
**/Thumbs.db

# 7. IDEs & Editors
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp

# 8. Logs & Docker
**/*.log
**/*.pid
**/.docker/


# Terraform & Infrastructure
**/.terraform/*
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*
.terraform.lock.hcl
dineflow-infrastructure/


# scripts (Recommended)
**/setup-cluster.sh
**/push_to_aws.sh